---
import CTAButton from './CTAButton.astro';
---

<section class="gradient-navy text-white py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-teal-500 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-gold-400 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 text-center">
    <div class="inline-block text-xs font-bold text-gold-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
      Ultima chamada
    </div>

    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] mb-5">
      Ou voce continua <span class="text-red-400 line-through decoration-red-500">perdendo dinheiro</span> sem saber por que...
    </h2>
    <p class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gold-400 mb-8">
      ...ou voce muda o jogo hoje, por R$ 97.
    </p>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-navy-100 leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Em 7 dias, voce vai olhar pros numeros do seu negocio pela primeira vez <strong class="text-white">com clareza total</strong>. E em 90 dias, pode estar como a Dona Marta: <strong class="text-gold-400">+R$ 35 mil/ano no bolso</strong>, sem vender 50% a mais.
    </p>

    <div class="mb-6">
      <CTAButton
        label="QUERO GARANTIR MINHA VAGA - R$ 97"
        size="xl"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-x-6 gap-y-3 text-sm text-navy-200">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        Pagamento seguro via Hotmart
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5 9V7a5 5 0 0110 0v2a2 2 0 012 2v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5a2 2 0 012-2zm8-2v2H7V7a3 3 0 016 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        Garantia de 7 dias
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M10 12a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z"/><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M.458 10C1.732 5.943 5.522 3 10 3s8.268 2.943 9.542 7c-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7S1.732 14.057.458 10zM14 10a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        Acesso imediato
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-10 text-xs sm:text-sm text-navy-300 italic max-w-xl mx-auto">
      "O que voce nao mede, voce nao controla. E o que voce nao controla, te controla."
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="bg-navy-950 text-navy-300 py-8 border-t border-navy-800">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 text-center">
    <p class="font-display font-bold text-white mb-2">Negocio no Azul</p>
    <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed">
      Copyright 2026 - Anderson Cruz. Todos os direitos reservados.<br />
      Este site nao e afiliado ao Facebook/Meta. Resultados variam de acordo com a aplicacao do metodo.
    </p>
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-4 text-xs">
      <a href="/termos" class="hover:text-white transition">Termos de uso</a>
      <span>&middot;</span>
      <a href="/privacidade" class="hover:text-white transition">Privacidade</a>
      <span>&middot;</span>
      <a href="https://instagram.com/anderson.fct" class="hover:text-white transition" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
